PAB PREPRINT SUPPORT INDEX
==========================

Purpose
-------
This file maps the current manuscript to the repository support layers and
reviewer-facing verifier commands. It is a navigation index, not a second
mathematical manuscript.

Canonical manuscript
--------------------
Mathematical source:
  paper/main.tex

Compiled manuscript:
  paper/main.pdf

Build command:
  cd paper
  lualatex -interaction=nonstopmode -halt-on-error main.tex
  lualatex -interaction=nonstopmode -halt-on-error main.tex
  lualatex -interaction=nonstopmode -halt-on-error main.tex
  cd ..

The layer notes inside L1/, L2/, and L3/ are frozen reference notes. For theorem
wording, use paper/main.tex. For support paths and commands, use this index and
README.md.

Repository roles
----------------
L1/        finite landscape and associativity reference layer
L2/        finite selection reference layer
L3/        selected-PAB operator, endomorphism, bridge, term-algebra, and
           companion-structure reference layer
mathcal_H/ global hidden-continuation theorem bundle
VERIFY_LOGS/ optional run logs

default reviewer-facing checks
------------------------------
Finite L1/L2/L3 quick audit:
  tools/run_quick_checks.sh | tee VERIFY_LOGS/quick_checks.log

mathcal_H default artifact audit:
  tools/run_mathcal_H_audit.sh | tee VERIFY_LOGS/mathcal_H_audit.log

mathcal_H audit including the heavier H2 focused artifact audit:
  tools/run_mathcal_H_audit.sh --include-h2-full | tee VERIFY_LOGS/mathcal_H_audit_with_h2_full.log

The default mathcal_H audit uses the light H2 coverage/consistency check. It
does not rerun the SMT solver. The focused H2 artifact audit is available via
--include-h2-full, and full recomputation commands are listed below and in
README.md.

Claim-family map
----------------
Normal form and basic structural reductions:
  Primary source: paper/main.tex
  Support role: structural finite proof in the manuscript, with L1/L2/L3 using
  the same normal-coordinate domain.

Global associativity atlas:
  Support layer: L1/
  Main verifier: python3 -S L1/scripts/verify_layer1_v3_final.py

Compact selection theorem and explanatory selection chain:
  Support layer: L2/
  Main verifier: python3 -S L2/scripts/verify_layer2_selection_final.py

Selected PAB operator, endomorphism, bridge, term-algebra, and companion layers:
  Support layer: L3/
  Main verifiers: python3 L3/scripts/verify_layer3_frontA.py ... frontH.py

Global hidden-continuation frontier:
  Support layer: mathcal_H/
  Main verifier wrapper: cd mathcal_H && PYTHONDONTWRITEBYTECODE=1 python3 verify_mathcal_H_bundle.py

Layer L1: finite landscape and associativity
--------------------------------------------
Role:
  L1 supports the finite landscape/associativity claims: global associativity
  range, endpoint loci, partition function, and related finite audit tables.

Main command:
  python3 -S L1/scripts/verify_layer1_v3_final.py

Primary scripts:
  L1/scripts/verify_layer1_v3_final.py
  L1/scripts/full_zq_verify.py
  L1/scripts/extremal_loci_verify.py
  L1/scripts/proof_skeleton_check.py
  L1/scripts/selection_bridge_verify.py

Primary tables:
  L1/tables/layer1_v3_Zq_full_assoc_distribution.csv
  L1/tables/layer1_v3_Zq_full_assoc_distribution_with_probability.csv
  L1/tables/layer1_v3_extremal_loci_counts.csv
  L1/tables/layer1_v3_extremal_loci_orbits.csv
  L1/tables/layer1_v3_extremal_loci_solutions.csv
  L1/tables/layer1_v3_fixed_diagonal_summary.csv
  L1/tables/layer1_v3_proof_targets.csv
  L1/tables/layer1_v3_column_blind_d000_table.csv
  L1/tables/layer1_v3_selection_bridge_claims.csv
  L1/tables/layer1_v3_status_registry_zq.csv

Scope guardrail:
  L1 controlled-H summaries are comparison/reference artifacts. The global
  hidden-continuation frontier is supported by mathcal_H/.

Layer L2: finite selection
--------------------------
Role:
  L2 supports the compact selection theorem and the explanatory finite selection
  chain: access-zero/column-blind rules, diagonal entropy, diagonal anchoring,
  local path-dependence, absorption transitions, pure C/J separation, and
  selector-independence audits.

Main command:
  python3 -S L2/scripts/verify_layer2_selection_final.py

